dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Juan Richardson. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Christine. How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim for an accident I was involved in.
I'm sorry to hear that. To proceed, I will need your policy number and a detailed description of the incident.
My policy number is five eight two zero one and the accident happened last Friday.
Thank you, Christine. Can you also provide me with the make and model of the vehicles involved in the accident?
Yes, it was a black sedan and a silver SUV.
Thank you for the information, Christine. We will process your claim and keep you updated. Is there anything else you need help with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your assistance, Juan.
You're welcome, Christine. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
